verses.text:
But I would ye should understand, brethren, that the things
\add which happened\add* unto me have fallen out rather unto the
furtherance of the gospel;

That at the name of Jesus every knee should bow, of \add things\add*
in heaven, and \add things\add* in earth, and \add things\add* under the
earth;

That ye may be blameless and harmless, the sons of God, without
rebuke, in the midst of a crooked and perverse nation, among whom
ye shine as lights in the world;

Circumcised the eighth day, of the stock of Israel, \add of\add*
the tribe of Benjamin, an Hebrew of the Hebrews; as touching the
law, a Pharisee;

That I may know him, and the power of his resurrection, and
the fellowship of his sufferings, being made conformable unto his
death;
